38
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,319
Mom.

39
00:02:14,319 --> 00:02:15,000
Sit down.

40
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,719
If you want to do something, come at me.

41
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:18,800
Don't touch my family.

42
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,360
I didn't.

43
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:23,159
You don't want money.

44
00:02:23,719 --> 00:02:25,800
Then you must want fame and status.

45
00:02:26,759 --> 00:02:28,080
I am not that materialistic.

46
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:29,719
I just wanted to save Mom.

47
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,400
You're not materialistic?

48
00:02:31,919 --> 00:02:33,400
If not, why save my mother

49
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,639
