50
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:37,240
Isn't it because my mother
looks wealthy,

51
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,759
while the bodyguard
is just a subordinate?

52
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:40,639
I...

53
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:41,800
I didn't.

54
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,919
You were once my brother's secretary.

55
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:47,360
