what my mother looks like?

56
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,400
Mr. Yan.

57
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:50,879
I...

58
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:53,319
You say you want nothing,

59
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:55,360
yet you accepted
the gifts without hesitation.

60
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,520
You also agreed to be her goddaughter
without a second thought.

61
00:02:58,879 --> 00:02:59,840
Bai Zhitao.

62
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:00,800
You

63
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,439
stay away

64
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:03,479
from my mother.

65
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:08,639
Mom.

66
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:10,680
I'm sorry, Auntie.

67
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:14,000
I think it's better
if we remain strangers.

68
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,240
Please don't get upset
with your daughter.

69
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,240
Xi.

70
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:21,759
Didn't Yan just say

71
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,120
it was all a coincidence?

72
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:24,520
Besides,

73
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,080
Zhitao saved my life.

74
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:28,280
And you,

75
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,800
