76
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,680
Did you ever think about how I felt?

77
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:33,520
Mom...

78
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,479
From what I see,

79
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:39,120
Zhitao is more like
my real daughter than you are.

80
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,240
You have truly disappointed me!

81
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:44,439
Mom.

82
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:44,919
Mom.

83
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:45,639
Mom.

84
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:46,520
Mom.

85
00:03:47,479 --> 00:03:48,159
