take some responsibility?

114
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,199
Quick, there's no time.

115
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:01,600
Dongfang Xi, don't you want
to save your mother?

116
00:05:04,959 --> 00:05:05,759
I agree.

117
00:05:07,460 --> 00:05:11,562
(Addicted to Toxic Love)

118
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:16,959
Yunzhou.

119
00:05:17,399 --> 00:05:18,399
Your girlfriend now

120
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:19,959
really thinks she's something.

121
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:21,199
I can't see her all day.

122
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:22,199
Where has she gone?

123
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:25,279
Is this Bai Zhitao's house?

124
00:05:27,519 --> 00:05:28,879
I am her boyfriend.

125
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,160
What is it?

126
00:05:30,639 --> 00:05:32,319
Bai Zhitao saved Madam Dongfang.

127
00:05:32,319 --> 00:05:33,879
