as her goddaughter.

133
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:54,439
Zhitao, you truly are my lucky star.

134
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,079
Yunzhou.

135
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,920
You've suffered a lot recently.

136
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,759
I want you to meet someone.

137
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:00,839
When you see her,

138
00:06:00,839 --> 00:06:02,040
