139
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:03,439
Who?

140
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:14,160
Dongfang Xi.

141
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:17,480
Ms. Dongfang is here
to apologise to you.

142
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:22,639
Dongfang Xi.

143
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,879
So you've come to this day.

144
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:28,439
I see the Dongfang family
doesn't value you much.

145
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:31,040
Even a goddaughter
can order you to apologise.

146
00:06:32,279 --> 00:06:33,079
Ye Yunzhou.

147
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,000
I really should apologise to you.

148
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,439
Of course.

149
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:39,199
